Name: pancreatic squamous cell carcinoma
Definition: A squamous cell carcinoma located in the pancreas.

Name: pancreas lymphoma
Definition: A carcinoma that is located_in the inside of the abdomen.

Name: tumor of exocrine pancreas
Definition: An endocrine gland cancer located_in the pancreas.

Name: pancreas sarcoma
Definition: A pancreatic cancer that is located_in the pancreas and that arises from transformed cells of mesenchymal origin.

Name: islet cell tumor
Definition: A pancreatic cancer that is located_in the pancreatic islet cells.

Name: pancreatic adenosquamous carcinoma
Definition: A pancreatic ductal carcinoma that derives_from squamous cells and gland-like cells.
